      "title": "Schools as usual from Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry said that the Ministry of Education decided to hold all public schools as usual on all five days of the week from the 15th of this month.",
        "The official further stated that this decision was reached during today's discussion between the education authorities."
